OL,3,CBurglar jailed after 40 minute roof
OL,4,Cstand-off with police
OL,6,FA burglar from Cheltenham has been
OL,7,Fjailed after a 40-minute roof stand-
OL,8,Foff with police.
OL,10,FWinston Allen climbed onto the roof of
OL,11,Fa house in the Leckhampton area after
OL,12,Ftriggering the victim's security
OL,13,Fsystem.
OL,15,FThe 59-year-old, formerly of High
OL,16,FStreet in Cheltenham, was seen on the
OL,17,Fsecurity system walking from one room
OL,18,Fto another with a torch, looking for
OL,19,Fjewellery and valuables.
