OL,6,FAfter police arrived, Allen attempted
OL,7,Fto flee by climbing onto the roof of
OL,8,Fthe property - where he remained for
OL,9,F40 minutes.
OL,11,FHe eventually agreed to come down and
OL,12,Fwas arrested and charged with burglary
OL,13,Fin a dwelling with intent to steal.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to the charge, and
OL,16,Falso admitted committing another
OL,17,Fburglary on the same night.
OL,19,FAt Gloucester Crown Court on Thursday
OL,20,F16 January, Allen was sentenced to two
OL,21,Fyears and four months in prison.
