OL,6,FInvestigating officer PC Sheer, from
OL,7,Fthe Cheltenham Vanguard Team, said:
OL,8,F"Being burgled can have a devastating
OL,9,Fimpact on victims leaving them feeling
OL,10,Fvulnerable in their own homes.
OL,12,F"It is hoped that Allen's arrest,
OL,13,Fcharge and sentencing shows how
OL,14,Fdedicated we are to taking burglars
OL,15,Foff the streets and helping to ensure
OL,16,Fthe residents of Cheltenham's homes
OL,17,Fare safe."
OL,19,FAs well as being jailed, Allen was
OL,20,Fordered to pay a victim surcharge of
OL,21,F#228.
